<div class="min-h-screen bg-base-100 p-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-box p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="max-w-md">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">%%PROJECTNAME%% Demo</h1>
          <p class="py-6">Welcome to the %%PROJECTNAME%% demo page. This page showcases Tailwind v4 and DaisyUI components with theme support.</p>
          <p class="pb-6">Use the theme selector in the top right corner to switch between different themes and see how they affect components.</p>
          <%= link_to "View UI Components", demo_ui_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Tailwind CSS v4</h2>
          <p>%%PROJECTNAME%% uses Tailwind CSS v4 for utility-first styling with PostCSS processing.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">Documentation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">DaisyUI</h2>
          <p>The project uses DaisyUI for pre-built components with theming support.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="https://daisyui.com/components/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">Components</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Catppuccin Themes</h2>
          <p>Features Catppuccin color palette integration with multiple flavors.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="https://github.com/catppuccin/catppuccin" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-base-200 rounded-box">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Development Only</h2>
      <div class="alert alert-info">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        <span>This demo page is only accessible in development mode.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
